                      }

                      function secret(){
                          const message = `Vall,

You don't just enter a room; you shift the entire atmosphere. There's something naturally powerful about you. The way you carry yourself. The quiet confidence in your eyes. The balance of softness and strength that lives within you.

You are the calm in my chaos. The light in my ordinary days. The reason I catch myself smiling without realizing why.

I didn't want to give you something ordinary. I wanted more than just words. I wanted something that feels like you‚Äîwarm, unforgettable, and full of life.

